text: ane be samudro sarakham nathi, a mitho che, je tarasa chipave che, piva mate uttama ane a bijo, kadavo, tame banne manthi taju mansa khava cho ane temanthi te jhaverata kadho cho, jene tame pahero cho ane tame ju'o cho ke mota-mota jahajo panine ciranara, te samudromam che, jethi tame teni krpa sodho ane jethi tame teno abhara mano
